</div>
<figcaption data-index="1892"><p data-index="1893"><span epub:type="pagebreak" role="doc-pagebreak" title="11-14" id="Page_11-14" data-index="1894"></span><span class="figureLabel" data-index="1895"><b data-index="1896"><a role="doc-backlink" href="#c11-fig-00014-1" data-index="1897" data-section-index="21" data-section-idref="c11-fig-00014-1" data-target-data-index="1821"><span style=" background-color: #127987; color: #FFFFFF;" data-index="1898">ILLUSTRATION 11.14</span></a></b> <b data-index="1899">Computing Depreciation after Revision of Estimated Life</b></span></p></figcaption>
