<td style=" vertical-align: top;" data-index="2801"><img src="https://ereader-books-prod.chegg.com/682/9781119503682/39c53495-be04-40a4-af01-80a39a7df223/OPS/images/real_world.jpg" alt="An icon shows two adjacent buildings in a square box." data-index="2802" data-size="%7B%22width%22%3A81%2C%22height%22%3A75%7D"></td>
<td style=" vertical-align: top;" data-index="2803"><b class="red" data-index="2804">Kellogg</b></td>
