<section id="h3_00075" data-index="4744">
<h3 data-index="4745"><span class="codeColorBlue2" data-index="4746">Problems</span></h3>
<hr data-index="4747">
<p data-index="4748"><b data-index="4749"><span class="codeColorBlue2" data-index="4750">P11.1</span></b> <span class="red" data-index="4751">(LO <a href="#lo_2" data-index="4752" data-section-index="21" data-section-idref="lo_2" data-target-data-index="976">2</a>)</span> <img style=" vertical-align: middle;" src="https://ereader-books-prod.chegg.com/682/9781119503682/39c53495-be04-40a4-af01-80a39a7df223/OPS/images/excel.jpg" alt="An icon reading text, “Excel”" data-index="4753" data-size="%7B%22width%22%3A46%2C%22height%22%3A22%7D"> <img style=" vertical-align: middle;" src="https://ereader-books-prod.chegg.com/682/9781119503682/39c53495-be04-40a4-af01-80a39a7df223/OPS/images/groupwork.jpg" alt="An icon reading text, “Groupwork”" data-index="4754" data-size="%7B%22width%22%3A78%2C%22height%22%3A19%7D">  <b data-index="4755">(Depreciation for Partial Period—SL, SYD, and DDB)</b> Alladin Company purchased Machine #201 on May 1, 2020. The following information relating to Machine #201 was gathered at the end of May.</p>
<table data-index="4756">
<tbody data-index="4757">
<tr data-index="4758">
