<p data-index="4930">The following transactions occurred during 2021.</p>
<p class="latin1" data-index="4931"><span class="label" data-index="4932"><b data-index="4933">a.</b>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span> On May 5, Machine A was sold for $13,000 cash. The company’s bookkeeper recorded this retirement in the following manner in the cash receipts journal.</p>
