<p class="latin1" data-index="6079"><span class="label" data-index="6080"><b data-index="6081">a.</b>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span> What is the definition of amortization?</p>
<p class="latin1" data-index="6082"><span class="label" data-index="6083"><b data-index="6084">b.</b>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span> What is the definition of impairment?</p>
<p class="latin1" data-index="6085"><span class="label" data-index="6086"><b data-index="6087">c.</b>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span> What is the definition of recoverable amount?</p>
