<figcaption data-index="6281"><p data-index="6282"><span class="figureLabel" data-index="6283"><b data-index="6284"><a role="doc-backlink" href="#fig-ifrs-11-2a" data-index="6285" data-section-index="21" data-section-idref="fig-ifrs-11-2a" data-target-data-index="6217"><span style=" background-color: #127987; color: #FFFFFF;" data-index="6286">ILLUSTRATION IFRS11.2</span></a> Computation of Component Depreciation</b></span></p></figcaption>
